@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor #FFFFFF
skinparam classBackgroundColor #F1F8E9
skinparam classBorderColor #33691E
skinparam shadowing true
[*] --> Cancelled
Cancelled --> OnHold : process
Cancelled : entry / log product
OnHold --> Reviewed : submit
Reviewed --> Processing : confirm
Reviewed : entry / log product
Processing --> Pending : process
Processing : entry / log product
Pending --> Archived : process
Pending : entry / log product
Archived --> [*]
@enduml